    /zcompressed.
get file = !File + "Care_Home_For_Source-20" + !FY + ".zsav".

* Housekeeping.
erase file = !File + "Care-Home-Temp-1.zsav".
erase file = !File + "Care-Home-Temp-2.zsav".

* zip up the raw data.
Host Command = ["gzip '" + !Extracts + "Care-Home-full-extract-20" + !FY + ".csv'"].

